                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-63-off366 t17960217-63-cd367"></join>, eleven pair of worsted stockings, value 20s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960217-63-victim647" type="victimName">
                     Samuel Richard 
                     Bennet
                  <interp inst="t17960217-63-victim647" type="surname" value="Bennet"></interp>
